summary: A SECRET cable from 1978 references an address and phone number in Miami, Florida, possibly related to staff actions or information files.
summary_one_paragraph: This SECRET cable, dated November 29, 1978, originates from an ADV C/LA staff member and is addressed to PRIORITY DIRECTOR, citing LA/MIAMI 29191. The message includes the identifier 1400 SW 16th Street, Miami, FLA. 33145, with the telephone number (305) 858-4406, and concludes with the end-of-message marker, indicating a communication likely related to staff actions and information files.
title: Cable Regarding Miami Address and Phone Number
